# This directory is populated at setup/build time by scripts/fetch-binaries.sh
# with the embedded adb + scrcpy toolchain. The directory itself is committed
# (via this placeholder) so the Xcode folder reference in project.yml resolves.
#
#   vendor/
#   ├── adb                       (universal binary from platform-tools)
#   └── scrcpy/{scrcpy, scrcpy-server, …}   (scrcpy v4.0 static build)
